â€¢Â Â Â Codifies the rules that your commit linter enforces.
â€¢Â Â Â Makes governance explicit â€” no â€œhidden rules.â€
â€¢Â Â Â Matches your Stack philosophy: rules arenâ€™t vibes, theyâ€™re written and auditable.
