â€¢Â Â Â Config-driven agents: no hardcoded definitions; pulls from agents.yml.
â€¢Â Â Â Orchestrator now supports both:
â€¢Â Â Â broadcast (parallel run).
â€¢Â Â Â run_sequence (pipeline).
â€¢Â Â Â Still uses toy tools for now, but ready to swap in functional ones.
