Â Â Â â€¢Â Â Â No hardcoded rules â†’ The logic is loaded from rules.json.
Â Â Â â€¢Â Â Â Every rule has enabled + description â†’ transparent governance receipts.
Â Â Â â€¢Â Â Â Auditable + configurable â†’ anyone can inspect or change the rules and instantly know why the audit passes or fails.

