âœ… What this does:
Â Â Â â€¢Â Â Â Runs on every PR.
Â Â Â â€¢Â Â Â Executes governance_audit.py against the latest commit (HEAD).
Â Â Â â€¢Â Â Â Enforces that all governance rules in rules.json are honored.
Â Â Â â€¢Â Â Â Runs the Governance Agentâ€™s own tests to prove itâ€™s valid.
Â Â Â â€¢Â Â Â If rules are violated â†’ the PR fails CI.

This makes the repo self-auditing by default â€” no code gets merged without passing governance.

