Hereâ€™s the full three-pilot scaffold (Finance, Healthcare, Civic) to drop straight into your repo. They mirror the ESG auditor: same receipt schema, sandboxed I/O, append-only ledger. Each has a minimal charter, stream, auditor, and test with at least one baked-in violation.

