Â Â Â â€¢Â Â Â dashboard_esg.html, dashboard_finance.html, dashboard_healthcare.html, dashboard_civic.html
Â Â Â â€¢Â Â Â index.html hub

Open index.html in a browser â†’ one-click cockpit for all dashboards.

